    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine - Model Years Late 1997 to 2003 - Crankcase, Crankshaft, Connecting
        Rods, And Pistons - Connecting Rods, Pistons and Piston Rings - Cleaning
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Cleaning</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Never use a caustic solution or a wire brush to clean aluminum pistons. Never use a bead blaster
                    on pistons.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Use a soap and water solution to clean the aluminum pistons. Soak the pistons, then clean
                the piston with a nonmetallic brush.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Clean all piston ring grooves thoroughly.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">The following disassembled components may be cleaned using a suitable solvent.</para>
            <randlist type="bullet">
                <item>
                    <para>Piston pins</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Piston pin retainers</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Connecting rods</para>
                </item>
            </randlist>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Thoroughly clean all connecting rod bolt holes and threads.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
